      .ccLetter.ccsc2
        p.first Let‚Äôs go into the details.
        p.header.thc1 1/ Content
        p
          span.italic How to build a modern day media company
        p First, I'm going to show you how to come up with a content strategy: Picking channels, standing out, distribution, tailoring, etc.
        p Then, I'm going to share!{' '}
          span.bold specific growth guides
          |!{' '}for!{' '}
          spam.italic Twitter, Instagram, LinkedIn, YouTube, TikTok, newsletters, podcasts, SEO
          | .
        p.header.thc1 2/ Ads
        p
          span.italic How to run high-performance ads.
        p We're going to set up an ad strategy from scratch for a B2B and B2C startup. Then we're going to turn this strategy into!{' '}
          span.italic REAL
          |!{' '}campaigns.
        p The exact process: Choosing platforms, making ads, A/B tests, targeting, tracking, etc.
        p.header.thc1 3/ Sales
        p
          span.italic How to get your first customers with sales
        p I'm going to teach you how to find people whose problem you solve, write emails which get replies, set up demos, and make some sales!
        p And again, it‚Äôs going to be!{' '}
          span.italic REAL
          | . Real emails. Real deals. Real rejections.
        p.header.thc2 4/ Copywriting
          span.mobileCourse &nbsp;& Landing Pages
        p
          span.italic How to communicate your product so people actually care.
        p We'll start with the fundamentals: formulas, hooks, positioning, story.
        p Then, we're going to rewrite title after title (until you finally get the hang of it). And,!{' '}
          a(href="") Annie‚Äôs coming back
          |!{' '}&#129392;
        p Finally, we'll use what we've learnt to write a landing page that converts (a more detailed version of!{' '}
          a(href="") my free guide
          | ).
        p.header.thc3 5/ Onboarding & Churn
        p
          span.italic How to keep customers happier, longer
        p
          span.ccHigh.thc1 Acquisition
          |!{' '}and!{' '}
          span.ccHigh.thc2 conversion
          |!{' '}are great. But without!{' '}
          span.ccHigh.thc3 retention
          |!{' '}you‚Äôre pouring your good work into a bucket with a big hole in it.
        p This is where we fix that. You'll learn proper onboarding, customer education, retention-focused email sequences, and much more.
        p.header.thc4 6/ Loops
        p
          span.italic What if your main source of growth was existing customers?
        p Most people think you build the product!{' '}
          span.italic then
          |!{' '}you market it. Understanding loops means building the marketing!{' '}
          span.italic into
          |!{' '}the product.
        p We'll run through the different types, the best examples, then deconstruct real businesses and set up some loops ourselves!
        p.header.thc5 7/ Game Time
        p
          span.italic Finally, we're going to do it all for REAL
        p I've picked two businesses struggling with growth.
        p I'm critiquing their current marketing. Then, I'll show you!{' '}
          span.italic exactly
          |!{' '}how I'd grow them (and help them implement).
        p.inwardSpeech I don't want to be the pundit that wins every game but he's never played one ‚Äî Jos√© Mourinho
